Program: Discovery
Title: What If... We could stay young forever? 1/3
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p014yxvn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Mar 2013
What if we could stay young forever? It may be a fantasy, but age management is big business and some people will stop at nothing to roll back the years. Pills, scans, injections, extreme diets and brain training - there's a vast array of apparent solutions on the market - but do they work and are they safe? Is age "reversal" possible? Peter Bowes investigates. (Photo: A woman is covered with sheets of 24-carat gold, said to be effective for anti-aging care. Credit: Getty Images) Show less